definitions.definition: The strengthened vein down the middle of a flower petal or simple leaf or leaflet .
The continuation of the petiole of a pinnately compound leaf around which the leaflets attach.

main_definition: ( botany ) The strengthened vein down the middle of a flower petal or simple leaf or leaflet .
